"Power Source" ke baare mein bataya hai. Is project ke liye power source bahut important hai kyunki ye project continuous operation ke liye designed hai.

Microcontroller, sensors, GSM/GPRS module aur other peripherals ke liye 5V DC power source ki jarurat hoti hai. 
Ye power source car ki battery se provide kiya jata hai. Car battery generally 12V hai, isliye hum isse 5V ke liye regulate karna hoga.

Iske liye hum voltage regulator ka use kar sakte hain, jaise LM7805. LM7805 12V input voltage ko 5V output voltage mein convert karta hai.
Ye voltage regulator bahut hi reliable aur efficient hota hai.

Aur agar aapki car mein inbuilt voltage regulator nahi hai, to aap ek DC-DC converter ka use kar sakte hain, jisse aap car ki battery voltage 
ko regulate karke 5V DC output generate kar sakte hain.

Is project mein, power source ko reliable banane ke liye hum multiple safety features ka use kar sakte hain jaise over-voltage protection,
reverse polarity protection, aur over-current protection. Isse car battery aur connected electronics ke damage se bacha ja sakta hai.
